# REST Client manual probes.
# Run with the "REST Client" VS Code extension.

@host = http://localhost:5001/mini-serverless-dev/us-central1
@audit_host = http://localhost:8082

### Healthcheck (firebase function)
GET {{host}}/healthcheck

### Create user (firebase callable, requires auth in real life)
POST {{host}}/createUser
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "displayName": "Alice"
}

### Audit (python cloud function)
POST {{audit_host}}/audit_handler
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "user.created",
  "user_id": "u1",
  "payload": { "email": "alice@example.com" }
}
